name: Everything is Sex
description: A red light district in a cyberpunk megalopolis. Procedurally generated using cell noise displacement textures applied to different layers of geometry with added holograms, neon lights, traffic, and atmospheric effects. Rendered in Blender Eevee. Featured OBJKT: #270140 "SEXXX DREAMS" by Fracto (@visualfracto). By Lucius Felimus: https://www.luciusfelimus.com/
